title: Ancient Aliens - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 5/3/22

description:
George Noory and author Paul Wallis discuss his theory that many ancient civilizations throughout Earth's history have had contact with alien races that helped humans rebuild after global catastrophes, and why religions and governments are covering up the existence of aliens.
